OL,5,Ccareer
OL,7,FWales international is set to play her
OL,8,Ffinal match after announcing her
OL,9,Fretirement from rugby earlier this
OL,10,Fweek.
OL,12,FThe 34-year-old has won 78 caps and
OL,13,Fplayed in four World Cups, with her
OL,14,Ffinal test match being at the WXV1
OL,15,Ftournament in 2023.
OL,17,FHarries' farewell appearance will be
OL,18,Ffor Welsh side Brython Thunder against
OL,19,FCeltic Challenge opponents Gwalia
OL,20,FLightning in Llanelli on today (3
OL,21,FMarch).
