OL,7,F"Life isn't always perfect, and if I
OL,8,Fwas younger I would relish the
OL,9,Fopportunity young players now have to
OL,10,Fachieve their dreams."
OL,12,Fadded: "Sioned's standing in the game
OL,13,Fis without question, and she has given
OL,14,Fso much to Wales and the jersey.
OL,16,F"To play in four World Cups is a stamp
OL,17,Fof her quality and determination and
OL,18,Fis a feat that won't be matched by
OL,19,Fmany players in the game.
